                  </hi>. I am in the service of a pawnbroker, in Drury-lane. I have a piece of kerseymere taken in from a person of the name of Hagan.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18370508-name-389" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18370508-name-389" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18370508-name-389" type="surname" value="HAGAN"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18370508-name-389" type="given" value="MARTIN"></interp>MARTIN HAGAN</persName>
                  </hi>. I have known the prisoner about a year and a half—he asked me to do little jobs for him—I never pawned any thing for him except this—I gave the money to him—I took it to a pawnbroker in Drury-lane.</p>
               <p>
